Values.value: SELECT DF.*,UD.USER_NAME FROM IX_DYNAMIC_FORM DF INNER JOIN (SELECT FORM_ID, MAX(VERSION) AS version FROM IX_DYNAMIC_FORM GROUP BY FORM_ID) D ON DF.FORM_ID = D.FORM_ID AND DF.VERSION = D.version join IX_USER_DETAILS UD on DF.LAST_UPDATED_BY = UD.USER_ID WHERE DF.FORM_ID='%formId%' ORDER BY DF.ID DESC
